Just that.

34
00:02:05,279 --> 00:02:06,000
What?

35
00:02:06,000 --> 00:02:06,720
You don't understand?

36
00:02:06,720 --> 00:02:08,839
How can I understand
when you didn't say anything?

37
00:02:08,880 --> 00:02:10,039
It's just that.

38
00:02:10,039 --> 00:02:11,119
Which? What?

39
00:02:11,320 --> 00:02:12,399
You don't know that?

40
00:02:12,399 --> 00:02:13,800
Which? I really don't know.

41
00:02:19,039 --> 00:02:20,279
Just...

42
00:02:20,559 --> 00:02:21,559
Just...

43
00:02:24,320 --> 00:02:26,160
Why can't I say it out?

44
00:02:26,240 --> 00:02:27,399
What can't you say?

45
00:02:27,440 --> 00:02:28,639
You can say anything.

46
00:02:28,880 --> 00:02:30,119
Why do I have to propose?

47
