I need to go out for a little while.

57
00:02:59,559 --> 00:03:00,440
Wait for me here.

58
00:03:02,839 --> 00:03:03,720
Siqi.

59
00:03:08,720 --> 00:03:09,559
Xiaosu,

60
00:03:10,479 --> 00:03:11,839
I apologize sincerely

61
00:03:12,759 --> 00:03:14,279
for suddenly disappearing

62
00:03:15,039 --> 00:03:16,399
and hiding the truth from you.

63
00:03:16,679 --> 00:03:18,639
You tell me the truth up until now.

64
00:03:20,679 --> 00:03:21,880
It hurts me

65
00:03:22,919 --> 00:03:24,440
so much.

66
00:03:26,240 --> 00:03:27,440
Can you forgive me?

67
00:03:37,919 --> 00:03:38,880
Sorry,

68
00:03:39,119 --> 00:03:42,239
but I don't think I can forgive you.

69
00:03:42,480 --> 00:03:44,079
I didn't have a choice at that time.

70
00:03:45,119 --> 00:03:46,880
I just wanted to protect you.

71
00:03:47,119 --> 00:03:48,200
Protect me?

72
00:03:48,480 --> 00:03:50,079
You think that hiding from me

73
00:03:50,760 --> 00:03:51,880
and running away from me

74
00:03:52,119 --> 00:03:54,399
were the best ways to protect me?

75
00:03:58,679 --> 00:03:59,239
Xiaosu.

76
00:03:59,279 --> 00:04:01,119
I'm not afraid of them at all.

77
00:04:01,359 --> 00:04:03,200
I'm not afraid of being followed.

78
00:04:03,440 --> 00:04:05,480
You know what I'm afraid of?

79
00:04:05,720 --> 00:04:08,040
You disappearing from my world.

80
00:04:09,440 --> 00:04:11,760
I was worried that I would not
be able to see you again.

81
00:04:13,480 --> 00:04:14,760
As long as I thought of

82
00:04:14,959 --> 00:04:16,320
how dangerous you were at that time,

83
00:04:16,760 --> 00:04:18,799
while I had no idea about it,

84
00:04:19,359 --> 00:04:20,839
I can't help feeling very sad

85
00:04:21,079 --> 00:04:22,359
and self-condemned.

86
00:04:22,799 --> 00:04:23,600
I really hope that

87
00:04:23,839 --> 00:04:26,079
the person who was there for you was me.

88
00:04:27,040 --> 00:04:28,799
Two people who love each other

89
00:04:29,040 --> 00:04:31,000
should face everything together,

90
00:04:32,399 --> 00:04:34,399
no matter being dead or alive.

91
00:04:42,399 --> 00:04:43,359
Qunfei,

92
00:04:43,720 --> 00:04:46,200
actually I know why
you don't want to get married.

93
00:04:47,119 --> 00:04:49,279
You want to wait until
you've become more successful.

94
00:04:51,559 --> 00:04:53,640
But I want to tell you that

95
00:04:53,880 --> 00:04:55,679
love can't wait.

96
00:04:56,519 --> 00:04:58,040
It's like the house price.

97
00:04:58,679 --> 00:05:00,359
If you don't make decisions quickly,

98
00:05:00,600 --> 00:05:02,040
you will regret it afterwards.

99
00:05:03,519 --> 00:05:05,720
I'm not the one
who I used to be anymore.

100
00:05:06,279 --> 00:05:08,200
I've thought through many things.

101
00:05:08,920 --> 00:05:09,799
People

102
00:05:10,279 --> 00:05:11,720
shouldn't be controlled by houses.

103
00:05:13,519 --> 00:05:15,440
We are poor and we can't
afford buying an apartment,

104
00:05:15,679 --> 00:05:16,920
but we can rent one.

105
00:05:17,119 --> 00:05:17,640
If you think it's too stressful

106
00:05:17,640 --> 00:05:19,440
to live in Shanghai,

107
00:05:19,640 --> 00:05:22,640
we can go to Australia together.

108
00:05:22,880 --> 00:05:24,480
We can be a farm owner,

109
00:05:24,799 --> 00:05:27,640
or we can buy a cheap car

110
00:05:27,839 --> 00:05:29,440
and travel around the world.

111
00:05:29,679 --> 00:05:31,359
We can be a citizen of the world.

112
00:05:33,679 --> 00:05:34,679
Qunfei,

113
00:05:35,440 --> 00:05:37,760
I'm saying all these
to let you know that

114
00:05:38,920 --> 00:05:40,720
it's OK that we can't
afford an apartment now.

115
00:05:41,920 --> 00:05:43,160
For me,

116
00:05:44,079 --> 00:05:45,200
home is wherever

117
00:05:45,640 --> 00:05:46,839
you are.

118
00:05:49,160 --> 00:05:51,720
I used to think that

119
00:05:51,959 --> 00:05:54,239
two people have to
enjoy themselves in marriage.

120
00:05:55,480 --> 00:05:57,160
But now I know that

121
00:05:58,079 --> 00:05:59,119
marriage

122
00:05:59,839 --> 00:06:01,839
requires the effort of two people.

123
00:06:05,359 --> 00:06:06,440
Qunfei,

124
00:06:08,600 --> 00:06:10,119
let's work hard together.

125
00:06:41,760 --> 00:06:42,799
Qunfei.

126
00:06:43,480 --> 00:06:45,200
He Qunfei, come back!

127
00:06:51,679 --> 00:06:52,720
He Qunfei.

128
00:06:55,679 --> 00:06:56,880
He Qunfei.

129
00:07:24,000 --> 00:07:25,040
From now on,

130
00:07:25,519 --> 00:07:26,559
no matter what happens,

131
00:07:26,559 --> 00:07:28,000
I will tell you immediately

132
00:07:28,000 --> 00:07:28,920
and I won't hide anything from you.

133
00:07:29,920 --> 00:07:31,000
Do we really have

134
00:07:33,160 --> 00:07:35,119
a future together?

135
00:07:35,679 --> 00:07:37,760
I've been thinking

136
00:07:38,399 --> 00:07:41,119
if we should actually be together.

137
00:07:51,480 --> 00:07:52,440
Xiaosu,

138
00:07:53,040 --> 00:07:54,600
do you know how long I've waited

139
00:07:55,279 --> 00:07:57,200
to hug you like this?

140
00:07:58,039 --> 00:07:59,960
I've never wanted to be apart from you.

141
00:08:01,640 --> 00:08:04,080
Thank you for telling me these,

142
00:08:05,599 --> 00:08:06,599
but

143
00:08:07,799 --> 00:08:09,119
I'm really tired.

144
00:08:11,039 --> 00:08:12,559
I want to be alone for a while.

145
00:08:13,159 --> 00:08:14,320
Maybe

146
00:08:16,239 --> 00:08:18,599
it's better for us to be friends.

147
00:08:47,039 --> 00:08:48,000
Siqi.

148
00:08:51,159 --> 00:08:52,440
Don't talk to me.

149
00:08:52,919 --> 00:08:54,400
I don't want to see you anymore.

150
00:08:54,400 --> 00:08:55,280
Siqi, listen to me.

151
00:08:55,400 --> 00:08:56,239
He Qunfei,

152
00:08:56,440 --> 00:08:57,679
