tell me all these reasons.

173
00:09:38,599 --> 00:09:39,520
I'm here and

174
00:09:41,000 --> 00:09:42,840
you don't need to worry about all these.

175
00:09:43,080 --> 00:09:44,919
Siqi, I've thought it through.

176
00:09:45,200 --> 00:09:46,799
Thank you for giving me confidence.

177
00:09:47,080 --> 00:09:48,640
We can't afford
an apartment in 10 years,

178
00:09:48,880 --> 00:09:50,520
but it doesn't mean we still
can't afford one in 50 years.

179
00:09:50,719 --> 00:09:52,000
But on top of it,

180
00:10:00,760 --> 00:10:01,919
you need to be my wife.

181
00:10:07,400 --> 00:10:08,400
Marry me.

182
00:11:05,200 --> 00:11:05,880
He Qunfei,

183
00:11:07,640 --> 00:11:08,479
what's that?

184
00:11:10,039 --> 00:11:11,440
Proposal ring for men.

185
00:11:12,239 --> 00:11:13,080
You've never seen one, right?

186
00:11:14,960 --> 00:11:15,960
Are you saying that

187
00:11:16,520 --> 00:11:17,719
Siqi proposed to you?

188
00:11:17,919 --> 00:11:18,919
It's embarrassing

189
00:11:19,000 --> 00:11:20,119
to say it.

190
00:11:20,559 --> 00:11:21,679
At first,

191
00:11:21,760 --> 00:11:23,159
I was shy.

192
00:11:23,239 --> 00:11:24,039
But I was surprised that

193
00:11:24,119 --> 00:11:25,799
she was very open-minded as a girl

194
00:11:26,039 --> 00:11:27,599
and proposed to me.

195
00:11:28,080 --> 00:11:29,039
But

196
00:11:29,320 --> 00:11:30,960
I also gave her

197
00:11:31,039 --> 00:11:33,239
