198
00:11:33,559 --> 00:11:34,840
So it was like a mutual proposal.

199
00:11:35,320 --> 00:11:36,919
So she doesn't care about
the house problem anymore?

200
00:11:37,719 --> 00:11:39,479
She said it by herself.

201
00:11:39,679 --> 00:11:40,760
If she didn't mention it,

202
00:11:40,840 --> 00:11:42,119
it would be stuck in my mind.

203
00:11:43,159 --> 00:11:44,080
Mr. Lei,

204
00:11:44,400 --> 00:11:47,760
now I'm your predecessor
in relationships.

205
00:11:47,840 --> 00:11:49,479
For love,

206
00:11:49,719 --> 00:11:52,559
