233
00:12:44,719 --> 00:12:45,640
Alright.

234
00:12:45,919 --> 00:12:47,000
Thank you for your trust.

235
00:12:47,479 --> 00:12:49,719
I will prepare a great speech.

236
00:12:50,559 --> 00:12:51,599
Thank you, Mr. Lei.

237
00:12:52,679 --> 00:12:53,719
