238
00:12:53,840 --> 00:12:54,640
Sure.

239
00:12:57,520 --> 00:12:58,679
Chase after it.

240
00:13:06,039 --> 00:13:06,719
Here I come.

241
00:13:09,440 --> 00:13:10,239
Stop.

242
00:13:10,719 --> 00:13:11,520
Let's have a rest.

243
00:13:12,239 --> 00:13:13,080
I'm so tired.

244
00:13:16,039 --> 00:13:16,840
You're quite a match now!

245
00:13:17,520 --> 00:13:18,119
You've made great progress.

246
00:13:19,559 --> 00:13:20,359
Bro,

247
00:13:21,000 --> 00:13:22,919
you seem a little distracted today.

248
00:13:23,640 --> 00:13:24,440
Tell me,

249
00:13:24,679 --> 00:13:25,919
why did you come to me

250
00:13:26,119 --> 00:13:27,039
so urgently?

251
00:13:28,400 --> 00:13:29,200
I...

252
00:13:33,400 --> 00:13:35,200
It seems the entry requirements here

253
00:13:35,280 --> 00:13:36,400
are getting higher and higher.

254
00:13:36,960 --> 00:13:38,799
There are more and more
beautiful girls here.

255
00:13:40,280 --> 00:13:41,080
Shangguan.

256
00:13:42,679 --> 00:13:43,479
Shangguan.

257
00:13:44,559 --> 00:13:45,280
What?

258
00:13:46,479 --> 00:13:47,320
Let me ask you.

259
00:13:48,960 --> 00:13:49,880
How...

260
00:13:50,320 --> 00:13:51,280
can you...

261
00:13:51,640 --> 00:13:52,919
make a girl...

262
00:13:53,719 --> 00:13:54,640
like you?

263
00:13:55,000 --> 00:13:56,320
Am I hearing it correctly?

264
00:13:56,719 --> 00:13:58,520
You're consulting me
for going after girls?

265
00:13:58,679 --> 00:14:00,320
