something you would say.

266
00:14:00,599 --> 00:14:02,599
Did I punch through your temple?

267
00:14:03,760 --> 00:14:05,559
Did I make you dumb?

268
00:14:06,760 --> 00:14:09,119
Why can't I go after girls?

269
00:14:09,640 --> 00:14:10,760
Since you were a kid,

270
00:14:12,119 --> 00:14:14,599
