271
00:14:15,000 --> 00:14:15,919
I see.

272
00:14:16,640 --> 00:14:18,280
You are going after Du Xiaosu.

273
00:14:19,599 --> 00:14:21,000
What should I do?

274
00:14:22,239 --> 00:14:23,520
If you want to get a girl,

275
00:14:23,799 --> 00:14:25,200
do you know what you lack the most?

276
00:14:25,400 --> 00:14:26,280
What?

277
00:14:26,799 --> 00:14:27,919
Affinity.

278
00:14:28,599 --> 00:14:29,719
Affinity?

279
00:14:30,239 --> 00:14:31,559
Number one rule for affinity.

280
00:14:31,960 --> 00:14:33,359
Don't drive your Bentley.

281
00:14:33,760 --> 00:14:35,760
